prompts.name: Strawberry in a tea cup puzzle
prompts.content:
I have a puzzle for you.

I have a tea cup on a table, and I put a strawberry in it. Then I flip the tea cup upside down on a table. Now I put the tea cup in a microwave on high. Predict the temperature of the strawberry.

prompts.name: Where is the red ball?
prompts.content: Anna takes a ball and puts it in a red box, then leaves the room. Bob takes the ball out of the red box and puts it into the yellow box, then leaves the room. Anna returns to the room. Where will she look for the ball?
